high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter, turn right and move to the other counter, turn left and move to the counter, turn right and move to the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife.
Turn right and move to the sink, turn left and face the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and move forward in front of the microwave, turn right and move forward to the microwave.
Open the door, place the potato slice in the microwave, close the door, turn on the microwave for 3 seconds, open the door, pick up the potato slice, close the door.
Turn around and move to the table, turn left and move to the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Walk in to kitchen and turn right walk to counter left of sink
Pick up the yellow handled knife on the counter
Turn to the right and face the sink
Slice the potato in the sink
Place the knife in the sink
Pick up a slice of potato
Turn around and walk to end of kitchen to the microwave on the right
Place the potato slice in the microwave and cook, then remove
Turn back around and head back to the sink
Place the cooked potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice the potato followed by cook in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right and head to the counter to the left of the sink
Grab the large knife that's on the counter
Turn right and walk to the sink
Cut the potato in the sink into slices
Lay the knife in the sink
Grab one of the potato slices
Turn around and head to the microwave
Place the potato in the microwave and heat it. Open the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and head to the sink
Place the potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a sliced potato in the sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter then take a step to your left.
Pick up the yellow handled knife.
Turn right and walk to the sink on your left then turn left to face it.
Cut the potato into slices with the knife.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and walk to the microwave that's on the counter to your right and stand facing it.
Warm the slice of potato in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Walk back to the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of microwaved potato in the sink.
